content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1260.21 - Acts of commission or omission endangering persons or property prohibited

State Regulations

No person in or upon any air terminal shall do or omit
to do any act if the doing or omission thereof endangers unreasonably or is
likely to endanger unreasonably persons or property. Notes
